Package: ThemeScope
Title: Social Representation Analysis via Semantic Network Mapping
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("ThemeScope", "Authors", email = "themescope@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Implements the ThemeScope framework for detecting and visualizing social
    representations in large-scale digital text corpora. Combines sentence-level
    word co-occurrence networks with Social Representation Theory constructs:
    Prototypical Salience Index (PSI) for anchoring and Concreteness Score (CS)
    for objectification. Produces two-dimensional thematic maps that locate
    communities in a theoretically grounded representational space.
